      <title>委内瑞拉在最新一次政府清洗中逮捕前石油部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/venezuela-arrests-former-oil-minister-in-latest-government-purge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗有争议地连任后，委内瑞拉上周末拘留了前石油部长佩德罗·特莱切亚，这是该国有石油公司内部清洗的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/venezuela-arrests-former-oil-minister-in-latest-government-purge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 14:53:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普面临被免罪的“中央公园五人组”的诽谤诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/trump-faces-defamation-suit-from-exonerated-central-park-five</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 因在 9 月份的总统辩论中对 1989 年慢跑者强奸案中被错误定罪的五名男子（后来被称为“中央公园五人案”）发表的言论而面临诽谤诉讼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/trump-faces-defamation-suit-from-exonerated-central-park-five</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 14:48:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚提高中国廉价钢铁进口关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/colombia-hikes-tariffs-on-cheap-steel-imports-from-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于生产商抱怨廉价进口产品对当地就业造成威胁，哥伦比亚成为最新一个提高中国钢铁关税的拉美国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/colombia-hikes-tariffs-on-cheap-steel-imports-from-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 14:21:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉丁美洲左翼领导人未能兑现承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-21/latin-america-leftist-leaders-boric-petro-struggle-on-promises-popularity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他们上台是为了解决这个不平等地区的社会动荡。现在，他们的失败可能会为更加商业友好的政府的回归腾出空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-21/latin-america-leftist-leaders-boric-petro-struggle-on-promises-popularity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 14:00:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉丁美洲左翼领导人未能兑现承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-21/lideres-de-esquerda-falham-em-promessas-por-toda-america-latina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他们上台是为了应对不平等地区的社会动荡。现在，它的错误可能为更加有利于商业的政府的回归铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-21/lideres-de-esquerda-falham-em-promessas-por-toda-america-latina</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 14:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>失败的承诺正在给拉丁美洲左翼造成损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-21/promesas-fallidas-estan-pasando-la-cuenta-a-la-izquierda-latinoamericana</link>
      <description><![CDATA[进步领导人上台是为了应对该地区的社会动荡。但其政治和社会成就寥寥无几，为亲市场政府的回归铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-10-21/promesas-fallidas-estan-pasando-la-cuenta-a-la-izquierda-latinoamericana</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 14:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国就业改革将使企业每年损失高达 45 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/uk-employment-reforms-to-cost-firms-up-to-4-5-billion-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据对该政策的经济分析，英国工党政府的一揽子工人权利改革计划可能使企业每年损失高达 45 亿英镑（59 亿美元），小企业受到的影响尤为严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/uk-employment-reforms-to-cost-firms-up-to-4-5-billion-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:34:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院驳回总统解雇机构领导的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/supreme-court-rejects-bid-to-let-president-fire-agency-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院拒绝受理一项上诉，该上诉旨在让总统控制长期独立运作的机构，可能包括联邦贸易委员会和证券交易委员会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/supreme-court-rejects-bid-to-let-president-fire-agency-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:34:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院驳回上诉，特朗普阻止迈克尔·科恩提起诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/trump-averts-michael-cohen-suit-as-supreme-court-rejects-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院拒绝让唐纳德·特朗普接受其前律师兼调解人迈克尔·科恩的诉讼。科恩称，他之所以再次入狱，是因为他不愿承诺不公开批评他的前任老板。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/trump-averts-michael-cohen-suit-as-supreme-court-rejects-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:31:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普到访后，麦当劳告知员工其不支持政治候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/mcdonald-s-mcd-tells-workers-it-doesn-t-endorse-candidates-after-trump-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普周日访问宾夕法尼亚州一家餐厅后，麦当劳公司表示，它不会在总统选举中偏袒任何一方。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/mcdonald-s-mcd-tells-workers-it-doesn-t-endorse-candidates-after-trump-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 13:31:46 GMT</pubDate>
